---
title: Mild Indian Halloumi Curry with Roasted Baby Broccoli & Basmati Rice
description: Delicately spiced and luxuriously creamy, this mild curry is sure to hit the spot! It’s packed full of flaky white halloumi and roasted veggies, making it ultra satiating - serve it over fluffy basmati rice and dig in!

